data.description: SPECIAL OFFER: Receive $6,500 toward closing costs if closed with our preferred Lender. *MUST USE PREFERRED LENDER*    Stunning one-story home in the coveted Agave Trace Community. This well-thought-out, open-concept floorplan features tons of builder upgrades - tile throughout the main living areas, gorgeous oversized walk-in shower with dual shower heads, upgraded carpet in the bedrooms, subway backsplash in the kitchen and upgraded tile in the bathrooms. Tray ceilings greet you in the foyer and lead to the gorgeous kitchen featuring an oversized island, stainless steel built-in appliances, 5 burner gas stove and 42" in white cabinets. High ceilings and oversized casement windows allow an abundance of natural light that feature custom window treatments in the living area and custom shutters in the front room. Relax on the oversized front porch or the covered back patio with NO backing neighbors. Home also includes smart security system and irrigation.
